OL,3,CTeenager killed in 'blink of an eye'
OL,4,Cat New Year's Eve event, trial told
OL,6,FA 16-year-old boy was killed "in the
OL,7,Fblink of an eye" when he was stabbed
OL,8,Fin the neck at a crowded New Year's
OL,9,FEve event, a court has heard.
OL,11,FHarry Pitman was allegedly attacked by
OL,12,FAreece Lloyd-Hall, 18, in front of
OL,13,Frevellers who had gathered on London's
OL,14,FPrimrose Hill to watch fireworks over
OL,15,Fthe River Thames on December 31 2023.
