OL,3,CTeenager killed in 'blink of an eye'
OL,4,Cat New Year's Eve event, trial told
OL,6,FOpening his Old Bailey retrial on
OL,7,FTuesday, prosecutor Jocelyn Ledward KC
OL,8,Fsaid: "Every year, large numbers of
OL,9,Fmembers of the public gather on
OL,10,FPrimrose Hill to celebrate the turning
OL,11,Fof the New Year.
OL,13,F"But on New Year's Eve, 31 December
OL,14,F2023, revelry turned to tragedy in the
OL,15,Fblink of an eye.
OL,17,F"Harry Pitman, aged 16, was stabbed
OL,18,Fonce to the neck. He died almost
OL,19,Fimmediately as a result of that single
OL,20,Fbut deadly injury."
