OL,3,CTeenager killed in 'blink of an eye'
OL,4,Cat New Year's Eve event, trial told
OL,6,FShe said the injury was caused by a
OL,7,Fknife brought to the scene by the
OL,8,Fdefendant, Lloyd-Hall, who was also
OL,9,Faged 16 at the time.
OL,11,FMs Ledward told jurors that Harry and
OL,12,FLloyd-Hall were strangers to each
OL,13,Fother and had gone to Primrose Hill
OL,14,Fwith separate groups of friends.
OL,16,FBefore the defendant arrived, Harry
OL,17,Fhad chatted with a special constable
OL,18,Fwho noted that he "physically bounced
OL,19,Fover" and seemed "overall positive in
OL,20,Fhis attitude towards police".
