OL,3,CTeenager killed in 'blink of an eye'
OL,4,Cat New Year's Eve event, trial told
OL,6,FWhen Harry's friend became involved in
OL,7,Fan altercation, Harry was seen on
OL,8,Fpolice body-worn video trying to calm
OL,9,Fhim down, jurors heard.
OL,11,FHe went on to engage in a friendly
OL,12,Fconversation with a man watching the
OL,13,Ffireworks and gave him a "fist bump",
OL,14,Fthe court was told.
OL,16,FLloyd-Hall, from Westminster, has
OL,17,Fdenied murder and an alternative
OL,18,Fcharge of manslaughter.
