OL,3,CTeenager killed in 'blink of an eye'
OL,4,Cat New Year's Eve event, trial told
OL,6,FMr Justice Cavanagh told jurors in the
OL,7,Fretrial that Lloyd-Hall's defence
OL,8,Fwould be that he thought the knife was
OL,9,Fcovered by a sheaf when he struck
OL,10,FHarry and that he acted in self
OL,11,Fdefence or defence of others.
OL,13,FThe retrial continues.
